Author-Name: Paolo Siconolfi 
Title: Recursive Equilibrium in Stochastic Overlapping-Generations Economies 
Abstract:
				 We prove the generic existence of a
 recursive equilibrium for overlapping-generations economies with
 uncertainty. "Generic" here means in a residual set of utilities and
 endowments. The result holds provided there is a sufficient number of
 potentially different individuals within each cohort. Copyright  2010 The Econometric Society. 
